{"tid":2507593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大內地碩士生涉與男童肛交 今提堂准保釋候訊","createTime":"2021-04-28T06:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T07:28:56.000Z","uid":136994,"like":47,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d32583efa9bf6ab15c7f93e66926e2cc6c0d29c2","tid":2507593,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/PCMEXIM2EZBR3DMZKZP3JQUVEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FPCMEXIM2EZBR3DMZKZP3JQUVEE%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=35b38fda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FPCMEXIM2EZBR3DMZKZP3JQUVEE%2F&h=65e949b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/PCMEXIM2EZBR3DMZKZP3JQUVEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n由廣州抵港僅兩個月的科大內地碩士生，涉於上月至本月間在尖沙嘴加拿分道香檳大廈內與一名男童肛交，被控一項與16歲以下男子作出肛交罪，案件今於九龍城裁判法院提堂。被告暫時毋須答辯，主任裁判官嚴舜儀應控方申請，將案件押後至6月23日再訊。被告獲准以現金三萬元及人事一萬元保釋候訊，其間不得接觸控方證人、每周三次向警方報到，並須交出旅遊證件，不得離港。"},{"pid":"4029ed4fe86e83edf191cc3155c7dc5a6e988d70","tid":2507593,"uid":110043,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"支那賤種"},{"pid":"73d9d7f31dd142ce48e357dfa160afaec3b457dc","tid":2507593,"uid":42188,"like":57,"dislike":25,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"支那來港，即係藍啦<br />\n16歲以下男生，即係黃啦<br />\n<br />\n結局: 男生用肛門強姦支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b362da3303f2ececc870979dc6d478ea871edde","tid":2507593,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":20,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"基佬=陷家剷"},{"pid":"c70e413201bb1a6b78602e3f6383f2cfdd168b33","tid":2507593,"uid":122167,"like":11,"dislike":17,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28